    <summary>Microsoft build of OpenJDK</summary>
    <description>This package installs the latest LTS version of the Microsoft Build of OpenJDK.

Unlike this meta-package, the following install a specific major version:

- [microsoft-openjdk11](https://community.chocolatey.org/packages/microsoft-openjdk11) - OpenJDK 11 (LTS)
- [microsoft-openjdk17](https://community.chocolatey.org/packages/microsoft-openjdk17) - OpenJDK 17 (LTS)
- [microsoft-openjdk-21](https://community.chocolatey.org/packages/microsoft-openjdk-21) - OpenJDK 21 (LTS)
- [microsoft-openjdk25](https://community.chocolatey.org/packages/microsoft-openjdk25) - OpenJDK 25

## Install Options

Custom install directory:

```
choco install microsoft-openjdk --params "'INSTALLDIR=C:\Program Files\OpenJDK'"
```

MSI properties: `INSTALLLEVEL=3 /quiet [INSTALLDIR="C:\your\path"]`
    </description>
    <releaseNotes>https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/java/openjdk/release-notes</releaseNotes>
  </metadata>
